==English==

===Etymology===
Derived from {{Fr}} ''[[pantalon]]'', itself derived from {{It.}} ''[[pantalone]], named after San Pantalone ([[w:Saint Pantaleon|Saint Pantaleon]]).

===Noun===
'''pantaloons''' {{pluralonly}}
# An article of clothing that covers the area from the [[waist]] to the [[ankle]].

